Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.75,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A racing second hand, tiny shooting stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:07.32,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:10.92,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's case is a Western legend!\NDon't put much stake in theories!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.53,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.43,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
